{"tid":1115492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美前總統卡特：中國「正在超越美國」 令川普感到不安","createTime":"2019-04-19T08:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T09:04:34.000Z","uid":75656,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b2b5e0bfe34981bc33f9e34dad118d78ae874e32","tid":1115492,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:31:04.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國前總統卡特（Jimmy Carter）14日表示，總統川普13日曾與他通話，告知他對中國越來越強大的經濟實力深感憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n《美國之音》報導，卡特14日在1次教會主日聚會上透露，川普13日打電話給他時表示，自己對中國「正在超越美國」深感憂慮，中國越來越強大的經濟實力，已使得這位美國現任總統感到不安。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，這是川普首次給卡特打電話，討論卡特提出的1個建議。卡特曾在今年1月給川普寫信，建議成立1個大約由6個人組成的專家小組，在幕後協助他改善跟中國的關係。<br />\n<br />\n卡特入主白宮期間，中美2國於1979年建交，卡特表示，自從1979年以來，中國跟任何國家都沒有打過仗，美國卻一直在打仗，浪費了3兆美元，而「中國在打仗上一分錢都沒有浪費」。卡特還指出，美國242年的歷史上，只有16年是太平的。<br />\n<br />\n現年94歲的卡特表示，他並不怕中國超過美國，但是這令川普不安。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2760161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2760161&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=5e4973bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2760161&h=0fcc2872\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2760161</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BoOufLK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoOufLK.png&h=fc5d0c5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57380ecaa89446f1be25b24d8be97566665e8444","tid":1115492,"uid":34562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"中國送哂d女俾班鬼佬屌，要還架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8462a647f0cc6c7fc786009a48e7747cc21ae61","tid":1115492,"uid":51828,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:54:20.000Z","msg":"在幕後協助他改善跟中國的關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248db216c7d3e7eaa06773b108df6d8359d2ea50","tid":1115492,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:56:37.000Z","msg":"呢啲飛機文真係百看不厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94e8caf29f1835e2461b10d77dee9211e1fe0c9","tid":1115492,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"「中國在打仗上一分錢都沒有浪費」，<br />\n<br />\nD錢貪曬落自己袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4725273e3dc346b87a443d8ac15bc6af93b16ca","tid":1115492,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57380ecaa89446f1be25b24d8be97566665e8444","tid":1115492,"uid":34562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"中國送哂d女俾班鬼佬屌，要還架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"唔知當年高美尼送咗幾多條女俾卡特呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}